  "lines": [
    "[section:Verse 1]",
    "Oh [G]give me a home where the [C]buffalo roam",
    "Where the [G]deer and the [A7]antelope [D7]play",
    "Where [G]seldom is heard a dis[C]couraging word",
    "And the [G]skies are not [D7]cloudy all [G]day",
    "",
    "[section:Chorus]",
    "[D7]Home, [G]home on the range",
    "Where the [C]deer and the [G]ante[Em]lope [A7]play [D7]",
    "Where [G]seldom is heard a dis[C]couraging word",
    "And the [G]skies are not [D7]cloudy all [G]day",
    "",
    "[section:Verse 2]",
    "Where the [G]air is so pure, the [C]zephyrs so free",
    "The [G]breezes so [A7]balmy and [D7]light",
    "That I [G]would not exchange my [C]home on the range",
    "For [G]all of the [D7]cities so [G]bright"
  ],
